28:17.750 --> 28:21.500
[exhales] I think I said something like,
there was a smell, which there was,

28:21.583 --> 28:23.250
and that it could have been mold.

28:24.333 --> 28:25.917
You said our lives were in danger.

28:27.208 --> 28:29.125
[Caitlin sighs]

28:30.167 --> 28:32.667
And, I don't know, I guess
if you're feeling that way again...

28:32.750 --> 28:34.042
