29:10.792 --> 29:12.500
Okay, this is it.

29:14.583 --> 29:17.792
Miguel really wanted his parents
to move here, you know, to be safer.

29:17.875 --> 29:21.417
But, um, his mom's not
the biggest fan of the States.

29:22.542 --> 29:23.625
