29:29.000 --> 29:30.083
What do you think?

29:32.458 --> 29:33.542
It's perfect.

29:34.792 --> 29:35.875
[Caitlin] Great.

29:37.708 --> 29:41.167
Um, yes, you've got
a closet here, shelves.

29:54.083 --> 29:55.833
