that might help.

32:31.958 --> 32:34.833
-Okay.
-Okay. Just turn around.

32:38.625 --> 32:39.708
Let's see.

32:47.000 --> 32:49.417
-Okay. It's gonna hurt a little bit.
-[winces]

32:54.500 --> 32:55.583
[groans softly]

32:58.708 --> 32:59.792
