33:07.042 --> 33:08.250
Yeah.

33:10.750 --> 33:13.000
I should... I should put Emma to bed.

33:13.083 --> 33:14.208
Okay. Yeah.

34:01.250 --> 34:03.500
[laughs] I'm sorry.
I just... I couldn't resist.

34:09.625 --> 34:12.250
Hey, go back to sleep.
I can listen up for Josie.

34:12.333 --> 34:13.542
It's fine.

34:13.625 --> 34:14.625
It's okay.

34:23.625 --> 34:24.708
What?

34:29.167 --> 34:30.250
Nothing.

34:35.333 --> 34:36.417
Okay.

34:41.500 --> 34:42.875
[door opens]

34:44.333 --> 34:45.583
