34:55.208 --> 34:57.458
[thudding]

35:03.250 --> 35:04.333
What do you think?

35:06.250 --> 35:07.292
I love it.

35:09.417 --> 35:12.375
-Just like the one you made for Emma.
-[chuckles]

35:13.792 --> 35:15.333
