35:28.375 --> 35:31.083
I know. I know
most people don't care about that.

35:31.167 --> 35:32.667
[chuckles]

35:33.375 --> 35:34.375
[indistinct chatter]

35:36.875 --> 35:37.917
Hi.

35:38.000 --> 35:39.208
Um...

35:40.125 --> 35:41.833
