about not feeding her sugar at all.

35:58.083 --> 35:59.208
We did?

36:01.042 --> 36:02.125
Yes.

36:03.167 --> 36:04.917
Oh, I'm so sorry, Caitlin.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.792
I-I didn't remember that.

36:09.750 --> 36:11.875
-You...
-It's...

36:11.958 --> 36:12.958
Whatever you want.

36:13.042 --> 36:15.083
It's just, she might drink
a little bit less.

36:17.625 --> 36:20.083
-It's just, I clearly remember that we...
-Mom...

36:21.708 --> 36:22.917
We were playing.

36:30.458 --> 36:31.625
