36:45.917 --> 36:48.458
the stuff we push under the rug,

36:49.500 --> 36:52.750
conversations that we are known to have,

36:52.833 --> 36:55.083
and certainly not in the public square.

36:55.792 --> 36:56.833
The forbidden.

37:05.667 --> 37:06.750
[indistinct conversation]

37:08.083 --> 37:10.708
[laughter, chatter]

37:24.042 --> 37:26.083
[Polly] Well, multiple times a week.

37:26.167 --> 37:27.417
Right. Otherwise...

37:27.500 --> 37:30.667
