37:31.708 --> 37:34.833
Depression, anxiety,

37:34.917 --> 37:36.167
prostate cancer.

37:36.250 --> 37:37.458
-[Miguel] Cancer?
-Mm-hmm.

37:37.542 --> 37:40.458
