43:34.000 --> 43:36.000
She's pretending to be someone else.

43:37.208 --> 43:38.458
Who is she?

43:40.875 --> 43:42.583
Not who she's pretending to be.

43:42.667 --> 43:45.167
[people singing in Spanish]

43:50.000 --> 43:52.125
[cheering]

44:24.000 --> 44:26.208
[woman over phone] Hi, Leah.
